# Director's Lab — Frontend Environment
# Copy to .env.local only if you need to override the API URL.
#
# ── Normal usage (dev + production via Firebase Hosting) ───────────────────
# Leave VITE_API_URL empty in BOTH dev and production:
#   • Dev:        Vite proxies /api/** to localhost:8080 (see vite.config.js)
#   • Production: Firebase Hosting rewrites /api/** to Cloud Run automatically
# Do NOT set VITE_API_URL for a normal Firebase Hosting deploy.
#
# ── Override (bypass Firebase Hosting — e.g. direct staging/testing) ───────
# Set to your Cloud Run URL only if you are calling the backend directly
# without going through Firebase Hosting (rare):
#   VITE_API_URL=https://directors-lab-api-xxxx-uc.a.run.app
VITE_API_URL=
